    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "interesting. so if it's such a flawed setup, what do the people who actually support the UN say? is there any real intellectual argument for keeping the veto power, or is that just seen as a way for powerful countries to get away with whatever they want?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
